<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Contact Us - EliteEscapes</title>
    
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #006400;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 15px 0;
        }

        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .navbar .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .navbar nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
        }

        .navbar nav ul li {
            margin: 0 15px;
        }

        .navbar nav ul li a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .contact-section {
            padding: 60px 0;
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .contact-section h1 {
            font-size: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #006400;
        }

        .contact-section p {
            font-size: 18px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .contact-form {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .form-left, .form-right {
            width: 48%;
        }

        .form-left input, .form-left textarea, .form-right input, .form-right textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .form-left input:focus, .form-left textarea:focus, .form-right input:focus, .form-right textarea:focus {
            border-color: #006400;
            outline: none;
        }

        .form-left button, .form-right button {
            background-color: #006400;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 15px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .form-left button:hover, .form-right button:hover {
            background-color: #004d00;
        }

        .map-container {
            margin-top: 50px;
            width: 100%;
            height: 400px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #006400;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        footer .social-icons {
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        footer .social-icons a {
            color: #fff;
            margin: 0 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        footer .social-icons a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="navbar">
            <div class="logo">EliteEscapes</div>
            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/about">About Us</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/services">Services</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="contact-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Contact Us</h1>
            <p>If you have any inquiries or need assistance, feel free to reach out to us. Weâ€™re here to help!</p>
            <div class="contact-form">
                <div class="form-left">
                    <h2>Send Us a Message</h2>
                    <form action="/send-message" method="POST">
                        <input type="text" name="fullname" placeholder="Full Name" required>
                        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email Address" required>
                        <input type="tel" name="phone" placeholder="Phone Number" required>
                        <textarea name="message" rows="5" placeholder="Your Message" required></textarea>
                        <button type="submit">Submit</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="form-right">
                    <h2>Our Locations</h2>
                    <p>We have hotels in prime locations around India. Find us at the following addresses:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>New Delhi</strong> - Imperial Suites</li>
                        <li><strong>Mumbai</strong> - Marine Bay Hotel</li>
                        <li><strong>Bengaluru</strong> - Garden City Resort</li>
                        <li><strong>Jaipur</strong> - Royal Palace Hotel</li>
                        <li><strong>Goa</strong> - Ocean Breeze Resort</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="map-container">
                <iframe
                    src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d7345.569832874535!2d77.20829824350261!3d28.644800267671974!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x390d1d745658e2db%3A0x44762ba9f8067b5f!2sNew%20Delhi%2C%20Delhi%2C%20India!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1634936797402!5m2!1sen!2sus"
                    width="100%" height="100%" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy"></iframe>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="footer-content">
            <p>&copy; 2024 EliteEscapes | All Rights Reserved</p>
            <div class="social-icons">
                <a href="#">Facebook</a>
                <a href="#">Instagram</a>
                <a href="#">LinkedIn</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
